<h2>tailloss: Estimate the Probability in the Upper Tail of the Aggregate Loss
Distribution</h2>
<p>Set of tools to estimate the probability in the upper tail of the aggregate loss distribution using different methods: Panjer recursion, Monte Carlo simulations, Markov bound, Cantelli bound, Moment bound, and Chernoff bound.</p>
